Invocation Name: san francisco guide
des:
This skill will help you to know more about San Francisco.
It gives interesting places and things to do while you are in SFO. Such as local attractions, top five things to do. It even updates you with local SFO news sourced from New York Times.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
